element_texts.text: Dear Dr. Taylor- Thank you for your letter and for the editorial in the Daily News. Both are interesting. Mrs Morgan and I are spending a few weeks at Yellow Springs for a vacation, and your letter was forwarded to me here. Am writing Knoxville to put you on the mailing list. It is very helpful to have your interpretation of the TVA? especially in the Chicago Daily News. I shall be glad to read the others as they appear. It was a pleasure to have you and your daughter as visitors in our community, & to hear? the convention? there. Sincerely, Arthur Mayfair?
